<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Bayern, Markgräfin von Brandenburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt das Einverständnis von Erhard Haller und Ulrich Volland, Bürger zu Nürnberg, zur Freilassung ihrer Knechte und Herausgabe ihrer Habe durch Albrecht Tanndorffer, Diener der Adressatin, auf Wiederstellen mit und sichert Tanndorffer.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_226" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_226_r1l28">Frawn Elıſabeth Marggrefın ʒu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_226_r1l29">Gnedıge fraw als vns eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> aber </del> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l30">
<del rend="strikethrough">von erhart hall </del> / vvıe Jr mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> dem <expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> tan = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l31">dorffer beſtellt habt / des erhart <expan>hall<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vollands <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l32"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / knechten mıtſampt der hab / bıs auf <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tag ʒu geben etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l33">Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd haben mıt <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l34"><expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſıe Jr knecht mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l35">ſampt der hab alſo <expan>auſʒneme<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf ein wıderſtellen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l36"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> . vnd darauf ſol der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> tandorffer vor </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_227" id="112v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l1">vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt ſıcher ſein von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l2">
<add><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan></add> alſo daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch ſıcher ſein . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_line_1577134173980_1929">dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_226" id="112r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elisabeth, marggrefin zu <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc.
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ir mit
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> dem <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
                        Tandorffer bestellt habt, des Erhart <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Vollands,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, knechten mitsampt der hab bis auf <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>ost<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tag</q>23.03.1421</note>
</app> zu geben etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und haben mit
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt, die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz sie ir knecht mit sampt der
                        hab also <expan>auszneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf ein widerstellen
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>. Und darauf sol der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Tandorffer vor <pb facs="#facs_227" id="112v"/>uns
                        und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit sicher sein von der sache
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan></add>, also daz die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch sicher sein. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
